	o multilingual stories\, sing songs and do simple arts and crafts with the
	ir caregivers during the group time.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nLake City Branch
	\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is 
	not required.\n\nDetailed Description: Kaleidoscope Play & Learn offer a c
