	e.\, There is also a play time for children to explore various toys and pl
	ay activities.\, Children learn and explore through the use of art\, music
	\, toys and more. Families learn about their child&'s development and comm
	unity resources available to them.\, Thanks to our partner\n\nDenise Louie
	 Education Center .\n\nEvent Logistics: This group is open to children of 
	all abilities\, ages 0 to 5 years old.\, Kaleidoscope Play & Learn is for 
	Family\, Friend & Neighbor Caregivers\, Parents\, and the children in thei
	r care. This is not a drop-off program and it is not agood fit for daycare
	 centers\, preschools\, or other childcare organizations.\, Find out more 
