BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:LBP6LizdP0rvoftfqgQnn
SUMMARY:Small Frye: Storytelling + Art
DTSTAMP:20260327T061037Z
DTSTART:20260401T171500Z
DESCRIPTION:Registration will open approximately a month before the event. 
	Enjoy a lively retelling of a beloved children’s book\, then create art wi
	th loved ones using materials designed to spark tactile play and wonder. T
	he hands-on art activity\, inspired by "Priscilla Dobler Dzul: Water Carri
	es the Stories of Our Stars\," is designed to enhance the skills and devel
	opmental strengths of pre-K children in collaboration with their caregiver
	s. This Small Frye session features the picture book Goldilocks and the Th
	ree Dinosaurs by Mo Willems.  Small Frye is free\, but registration is req
	uired. Space is limited—sign up today! --- https://fryemuseum.org/calendar
	/event/small-frye-april-2026\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/deta
